criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Body Mass Index between 30 and 40 kg/m2;

          -  Obstrutive sleep apnea mild or severe;

          -  Sedentary.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Intake of any drug that interfere on metabolismo such for tyreoid or to lose weight;

          -  Be engaged in other treatmento for sleep apnea or obesity;

          -  Present another sleep disorder;

          -  Being shift work;

          -  Present any kind of kidney desease.
